{"tid":1448644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:49.000Z","uid":268394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c078c5a24d525145aacaf1949bab21db15c91344","tid":1448644,"uid":268394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:36:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"3a592b8c936797db55a7864827f5ea333fae3881","tid":1448644,"uid":268394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:38:03.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"e64ec01e711fa67bab9c9bbbb5d49444adc4e37b","tid":1448644,"uid":268394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T18:01:49.000Z","msg":"2"}]}